202
00:12:43,980 --> 00:12:44,900
Moka-san...

203
00:12:45,500 --> 00:12:47,860
Nejsem sobecká?

204
00:12:48,400 --> 00:12:51,050
Chtěla bych být navěky jen s tebou.

205
00:12:51,910 --> 00:12:52,640
Moka-san?

206
00:12:53,070 --> 00:12:53,920
Vadí ti to?

207
00:12:54,400 --> 00:12:56,810
Vůbec ne! Já taky...

208
00:12:57,780 --> 00:12:58,670
Tsukune...

209
00:12:59,180 --> 00:12:59,950
Moka-san...

210
00:13:01,030 --> 00:13:01,880
Tsukune...

211
00:13:02,460 --> 00:13:03,440
Moka-san...

212
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:05,110
Tsukune!

213
00:13:05,850 --> 00:13:06,900
Moka-san!

214
00:13:11,070 --> 00:13:12,220
Našel jsem vás!

215
00:13:12,870 --> 00:13:14,350
Ty jsi ten z odpoledne!

216
00:13:16,270 --> 00:13:19,030
